============================================================
  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Hepatitis B
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HBV
Transmission:Blood, sexual contact
Symptoms:    Often asymptomatic; jaundice
Treatment:   Antivirals (tenofovir)
Deaths/yr:   0.82M
Vaccine:     Yes (highly effective)
Discovered:  1965

Disease:     Influenza
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Influenza viruses
Transmission:Respiratory droplets
Symptoms:    Fever, chills, muscle aches
Treatment:   Oseltamivir, rest, fluids
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     Yes (annual update)
Discovered:  1933

Disease:     Diabetes Type 2
Type:        Metabolic
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Lifestyle
Symptoms:    Thirst, frequent urination, fatigue
Treatment:   Metformin, lifestyle, insulin
Deaths/yr:   1.5M
Vaccine:     No
Discovered:  1922

============================================================
  ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE & MACHINE LEARNING
============================================================

Concept:     Vector Database
Category:    Infrastructure
Definition:  Stores high-dimensional embeddings for similarity search
Year:        2019
Researchers: Pinecone/Weaviate/Faiss
Applications:RAG, semantic search, recommendation
Related:     ANN search, HNSW, cosine similarity

Concept:     Backpropagation
Category:    Training
Definition:  Computes gradients via chain rule through network layers
Year:        1986
Researchers: Rumelhart/Hinton
Applications:Training all neural networks
Related:     Gradient descent, automatic differentiation

Concept:     GAN
Category:    Architecture
Definition:  Generator vs discriminator adversarial training
Year:        2014
Researchers: Ian Goodfellow et al.
Applications:Image synthesis, deepfakes, augmentation
Related:     Mode collapse, discriminator, generator

